		<title>「人力エネルギー」　－　東西どこでも考えは同じ</title>
		<link>https://midori1kwh.de/2012/01/15/1120?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%258a%259b%25e3%2582%25a8%25e3%2583%258d%25e3%2583%25ab%25e3%2582%25ae%25e3%2583%25bc%25e3%2580%258d%25e3%2580%2580%25ef%25bc%258d%25e3%2580%2580%25e6%259d%25b1%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e3%2581%25a9%25e3%2581%2593%25e3%2581%25a7%25e3%2582%2582%25e8%2580%2583%25e3%2581%2588%25e3%2581%25af%25e5%2590%258c</link>
